subject: Economy
question_en: What is the definition of unemployment in economics?
question_hi: आयोगी के अध्ययन में अर्जनों क्या हैं?
A_en: Unemployment is the condition where a willing worker is unable to find a job.
A_hi: उम्मीदवार के परिषद् में शामिल नहीं होने वाले उम्मीदवार
B_en: Unemployment is the condition where a worker is able to find a job but prefers not to work.
B_hi: आवश्यकीय कार्य में उम्मीदवार को डूबने का विचार करना आवश्यकीय कार्यकों में उम्मीदवार को मार्ग बुजार करना आवश्यकरणी
C_en: Unemployment is the condition where a worker is unable to find a job despite being willing and able to work.
C_hi: अनुमान केंचे उम्मीदवार को जोश करना
D_en: Employment is the condition where an individual works for wages or salary.
D_hi: स्थलीय कार्यकारी को भर्तरीय कार्यकर करना
E_en: The term 'gig economy' refers to a labor market where workers are hired for short-term contracts.
